          "reviewBody": "Passed from this school in 2018. You know when you passed from a school then you can't able to tell any cons of that school😂😂 I don't why, but still I'm very attached with this school. Wish I could relive that life in school🤧.\n\nHey why don't you guys do a alumni meet, you'll get stories to motivate your upcoming batch. You'll also find that the Backbenchers who always scolded by each and every teacher😂😂. Became a successful person in life.",
          "publisher": {
