          "datePublished": "2018-06-27",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Its a good school overall speaking. I have personally studied here. For sports it has a big football ground, basketball court, volleyball court and badminton court. Also has a big swimming pool with regular swimming classes. Smart classes are also there. Teachers are friendly and helpful. But one annoyance about every private school is their fee which is always high. I rated 4 stars and not 5 just because of the fee which I think should be a bit less. Apart from that the school and its facilities are good.",
          "publisher": {
